OL,3,CHunt makes triple-lock pledge but
OL,4,Crefuses to commit to Waspi women
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FJeremy Hunt has promised the triple
OL,8,Flock for pensions will be included in
OL,9,Fthe Tory election manifesto but
OL,10,Frefused to commit to compensation for
OL,11,Fso-called Waspi women.
OL,13,FThe Chancellor said the safeguard
OL,14,Fwould be kept throughout the next
OL,15,Fparliament under the Conservatives,
OL,16,Finsisting he was confident the
OL,17,F"expensive" policy could be paid for
OL,18,Fthrough economic growth.
