OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FThe triple lock refers to the
OL,8,Fcommitment to raise the state pension
OL,9,Fevery year in line with whichever is
OL,10,Fhighest out of wage growth, inflation
OL,11,For 2.5%.
OL,13,FIt has become a hallmark of successive
OL,14,FConservative governments since it was
OL,15,Fannounced in 2010, but there has been
OL,16,Fa debate about its long-term future
OL,17,Fdue its costs.
