OL,3,CHunt makes triple-lock pledge but
OL,4,Crefuses to commit to Waspi women
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,F"Absolutely. We made that commitment
OL,8,Fto pensioners and we think it's a very
OL,9,Fimportant one," he told the BBC's
OL,10,FSunday With Laura Kuenssberg programme
OL,11,Fwhen asked if he could guarantee the
OL,12,Fmeasure would be continued.
OL,14,FLabour said it was "committed to
OL,15,Fretaining" the triple lock but party
OL,16,Fchairwoman Anneliese Dodds did not
OL,17,Fconfirm whether the policy would
OL,18,Ffeature in its manifesto when
OL,19,Fquestioned by broadcasters on Sunday.
