OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats accused the
OL,8,FTories of playing a "shameless
OL,9,Felection trick" over the safeguard and
OL,10,Fclaimed the party was "taking
OL,11,Fpensioners for granted".
OL,13,FElsewhere, Mr Hunt declined to promise
OL,14,Fcompensation for women hit by changes
OL,15,Fto state pension eligibility, amid
OL,16,Faccusations the Government failed to
OL,17,Fadequately inform those born in the
OL,18,F1950s about an increase in the
OL,19,Fentitlement age.
