OL,4,Crefuses to commit to Waspi women
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FSpeaking to broadcasters, the
OL,8,FChancellor denied pushing the decision
OL,9,Fto the right for a future
OL,10,Fadministration to deal with, as Labour
OL,11,Fenjoys a sustained double-digit lead
OL,12,Fin opinion polls ahead of this year's
OL,13,Felection.
OL,15,FHe said the issue highlighted by the
OL,16,FWomen Against State Pension Inequality
OL,17,F(Waspi) campaign was "genuinely more
OL,18,Fcomplicated" than others in which
OL,19,Fcompensation has been promised, like
OL,20,Fthe infected blood disaster and the
OL,21,FPost Office Horizon scandal.
