OL,7,FIt comes after a long-awaited report
OL,8,Fby the Parliamentary and Health
OL,9,FService Ombudsman (PHSO) that found
OL,10,Fthe changes to the state pension age
OL,11,Fwere not communicated adequately and
OL,12,Fthose affected should receive an
OL,13,Fapology and compensation.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/10
