OL,3,CHunt makes triple-lock pledge but
OL,4,Crefuses to commit to Waspi women
OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FAsked whether it was responsible for
OL,8,Fthe Government to leave "huge unpaid
OL,9,Fbills" to the next parliament, he
OL,10,Fsaid: "We had the ombudsman's report
OL,11,Fon Thursday, but we've also had a
OL,12,Freport from the High Court and Court
OL,13,Fof Appeal in 2020 that says the
OL,14,FDepartment for Work and Pensions
OL,15,Fbehaved completely within the law and
OL,16,Fdidn't discriminate.
OL,18,F"So it appears to say something
OL,19,Fdifferent and we do need to get to the
OL,20,Fbottom of that apparent difference
OL,21,Fbetween the two."
