OL,7,FHe added: "We want to resolve it as
OL,8,Fquickly as we can, but there's no
OL,9,Fsecret vault of money.
OL,11,F"The money we would pay in
OL,12,Fcompensation has to come from other
OL,13,Ftaxpayers, so we do have to take time
OL,14,Fto get this fair."
