OL,5,Cpayouts
OL,7,FCampaigners have demanded action over
OL,8,Fthe report, warning Prime Minister
OL,9,FRishi Sunak will be on a "sticky
OL,10,Fwicket" seeking votes from Waspi women
OL,11,Fwhen he goes to the country later this
OL,12,Fyear if he does not heed the
OL,13,Fombudsman's findings.
OL,15,FBut amid straitened public finances,
OL,16,Fpoliticians on both sides have shied
OL,17,Faway from commitments to payouts, with
OL,18,Fneither Labour nor the Conservatives
OL,19,Fsaying whether they would compensate
OL,20,Fthose affected.
